Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.13,0:00:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要拯救世界的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.60,0:00:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱离走向毁灭的大崩落危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.34,0:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不断旅行的里德，法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.77,0:00:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停留的海上都市·贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满了许多的迷团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在地下的“奈雷特福音”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.65,0:00:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.12,0:00:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有等待里德他们的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又将会如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.93,0:00:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第11话  可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.93,0:00:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜  可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜，你在哪里？  可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  又翘掉剑术的练习了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.67,0:00:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天艾克丝西亚大人就要来了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房间也是乱七八糟  真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.08,0:01:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天妈妈就要来看我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天妈妈就要来看我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还在唱歌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.96,0:01:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有够悠哉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.43,0:01:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是里德他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.87,0:01:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂~我们在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.89,0:02:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是又做出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.23,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么奇怪的事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一点印象都没有吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要一看到晶灵光涡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个人的感觉就会不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后接下来就会暂时失去记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每年都是这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年？你每年都看啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我一直瞒着你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实可莉娜我是贝鲁卡纽的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你想不到的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.22,0:02:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜是艾克丝西亚妈妈的独女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.19,0:02:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.13,0:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.63,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈拜托我这样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说希望让里德大人他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够看到晶灵光涡的现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我一定要设法把你们留在岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会隐藏身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们住在同一家旅馆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晶灵光涡很漂亮吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么从刚才都不说话啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不跟我解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么会在这个岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是可莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.23,0:03:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了什么不堪入耳的话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦~我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.97,0:03:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下子我嫁不出去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说什么？玛萝妮死了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.61,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.74,0:03:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死玛萝妮父母的仇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.41,0:03:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮虽然想要报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.84,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是却失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.88,0:03:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在逃出来的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了掩护我们离开就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.23,0:03:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是…她的仇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得可莉娜是不是还有印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她遭到了艾克丝西亚的控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我们这里把大晶灵夺走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.54,0:04:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人  艾克丝西亚她还说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要利用可莉娜的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的  一直骗可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是她的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.52,0:04:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜，你要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去见妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见了她之后我要证实刚才那些话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是都是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我实在无法相信！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到妈妈会欺骗可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然只是想利用我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在见到妈妈把话说清楚前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜根本就不相信那些话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…我现在就去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.26,0:05:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.17,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你们打算带我们去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别问那么多   给我走就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚把那些反抗她的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.89,0:06:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都抓了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也打算抓我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信妈妈会做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.93,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这其中一定有什么误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是有什么原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈才不会做那种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静一点啦，葵吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.94,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个是什么人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你们不是通缉中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德·哈谢尔的同伙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人又没有做什么坏事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会遭受通缉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是和他们同一伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！  趁现在快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们是里德·哈谢尔的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快抓住她们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！  在这里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.78,0:06:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是死心吧  你们无处可逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是可莉娜·索鲁珍特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是贝鲁卡纽的领主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是艾克丝西亚大人的女儿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撒谎的话也找个高明一点的谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜并没有说谎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让我看看你的艾拉拉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是赛雷斯提亚人的后裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.48,0:07:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个道地的赛雷斯提亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是她的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必会有很棒的艾拉拉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你叫做可莉娜·索鲁珍特吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人有直接下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈有下令吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果出现一个自称是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜·索鲁珍特的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当场格杀勿论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的假面具被揭穿了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.47,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定…不是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.54,0:08:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.38,0:08:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！  基尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是里德·哈谢尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万别让他跑了！  是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双撞掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤口又裂开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能找个地方好好治疗就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可利鲁岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.74,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有可莉娜过去住过的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我什么也没带就离开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.41,0:09:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该还有些药品和绷带才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜…好想回家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就去可莉娜家打扰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.06,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这伤要好好麻烦你治疗啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大晶灵已经趋于稳定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正继续进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.31,0:09:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与制裁之楔连结的作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预估在今天之内完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说出现了一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.11,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自称是可莉娜·索鲁珍特的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得有下令当场格杀无论的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果被她跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德·哈谢尔把她带离本岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.86,0:09:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可利鲁岛是位于贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.30,0:10:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边界的一个小岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了可莉娜的家以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.84,0:10:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一无所有的宁静地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和艾克丝西亚是分开住的啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过她偶而会过去那里玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带给我很多的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得“偶而”是多久一次啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约是一年两次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是那座岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面没有半只怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很适合居住的岛屿耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，可莉娜的家就在那一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怪兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子里面好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风雷神剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你是…那个酒店的大叔嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我想像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的大多是从别的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移居到贝鲁卡纽的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是不愿服从艾克丝西亚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比预期的要来的多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导致收容所已经容纳不下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，记得在搭船的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船上的士兵是有这么讲过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此在这个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先把跟贝鲁卡纽的关系较薄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近才移居到这里的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丢给怪物来处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那却是最有效率的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.13,0:11:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是偏偏是选在可莉娜住的岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那也在她的计算之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实还有这个可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.71,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了防止可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我们回到这岛上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才安排这些怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过现阶段…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经陷入无法动弹的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加上有这么多的伤患
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我们要如何逃出这个地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面可是有一大堆怪物耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.13,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于可莉娜这个存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾克丝西亚从头到尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想拿来作利用而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样她未免太可怜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是事实啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.77,0:12:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些伤患的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以让巴鲁沙来搬运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这周遭的各个岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经安排怪物在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.61,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在到达安全的岛屿之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些伤患的体力会撑不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶~到底该怎么办好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚可莉娜对你们说了谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实可莉娜住在这里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈只来看过我两次而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.77,0:13:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…停留的时间也非常短暂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她大概不是我的亲生母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.52,0:13:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又没有其它可以让我喊妈妈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只有对自己说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为妈妈她太忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实这个地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有任何有关妈妈的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要回到这里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得…能够再当妈妈的女儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说可莉娜以后该怎么办好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还给里德大人添了好多的麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该何去何从呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂最喜欢唱歌时的可莉娜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信里德一定也跟我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.83,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何不唱歌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像平常那样很有精神的唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.24,0:14:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一座小岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住着一个可爱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩非常喜欢唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.71,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜搞不好可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.38,0:14:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮上里德大人的忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.53,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小的时候我一天到晚只知道唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就会挨奶妈的骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都偷偷跑进这里面唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他人发现到这个地方吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前住在这里的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有奶妈和可莉娜知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是…武器的数量真是惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然这些是武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就觉得好像是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦  可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.35,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有这些武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能够打倒所有的怪物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.19,0:15:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有这么多武器…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些是反对势力的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投入了数十名人力准备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为的是等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒艾克丝西亚的那天到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.37,0:15:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都平安无事  真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.41,0:15:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这些人救了我一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.71,0:15:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是反艾克丝西亚同盟的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反…艾克丝西亚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜  有件事我必须告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有关我妈妈的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经知道了是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，其实艾克丝西亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.33,0:16:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是你真正的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母亲在你出生后不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为船难去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时是艾克丝西亚大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捡到漂流到贝鲁卡岛来的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她发现你有控制晶灵的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就决定把你当自己的女儿抚养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.97,0:16:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目的就是等到有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到大晶灵的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好的利用你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:16:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道真相之后  心里就舒畅多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.95,0:17:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.39,0:17:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些可恶的怪兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快拿武器出去对抗！  是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.13,0:17:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂，你和可莉娜一起留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，可莉娜也要一起战斗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能够加入战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.48,0:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家来拿这些武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人  千万不要大意轻敌哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.44,0:17:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜你的家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意继续待在我身边吗？
